    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Queue is an interface; you can't explicitly construct a Queue. You'll have to instantiate one of its implementing classes. Something like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Queue linkedList = new LinkedList();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/java/concepts/interface.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Here's a link to the Java tutorial on this subject.</a></p>\n"
