    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Queue is an interface in java, you can not do that.</p>\n\n<p>Instead you have two options:</p>\n\n<p>option1:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Queue&lt;Integer&gt; Q = new LinkedList&lt;&gt;();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>option2:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Queue&lt;Integer&gt; Q = new ArrayDeque&lt;&gt;();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>I recommend using option2 as it is bit faster than the other</p>\n"
